        <abstract> 
<p>Ecstatic praise of CD and <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, which has transformed physiognomy.</p>  
<p>Sends his papers on sadness ["Dell’azione del dolore", <hi rend="italic">Gaz. Med. Ital. Lombarda</hi> (1866, 1867)]. Sends some observations on physiognomy.</p> 
